  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-top-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2561/order2/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; line-height: 1.8em; border-top-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tExcused<br />\n\t<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Excused\" target=\"_blank\">Excused</a> means to have permission to be excluded from an activity. Who is excused? What is the reason? What is the occasion?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They were excused... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) excused from class due to sickness<br />\n\t2) excused oneself in the middle of a meeting to answer an important call outside<br />\n\t3) excusing oneself after sneezing in front of others<br />\n\t4) a senior excused the mistake of a junior<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tAl quickly and smoothly excused himself from his enthusiastic fans. After going past a few people, he put his mask back on. This was when the hanging silky material as part of the d&eacute;cor became useful. The model managed to change his mask a couple of times. As he walked by staff members with masks, he would pick up one and put it on when he stepped in between the draping <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/fabric\" target=\"_blank\">fabric</a>. It did not take long before Al blended into the crowd completely once again. During this time, he kept track of his target.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/163122571751/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p731604/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p731604\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p733679/\">哈佛情商测试，满分200，你得了多少？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p733875/\">13句受用终生的人生格言</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p733814/\">英语中12个典型的中国式错误是哪些？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p733346/\">像娜塔莉波特曼般聪明？这5类书最能提高IQ</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p733967/\">心都萌化了！英国小王子轻吻妹妹</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p731795/\">美女们请注意！千万别在简历上附照片！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p732912/\">全球海选：生命中最寻常的幸福小事</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p733963/\">励志！英截肢姑娘变身美艳模特</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p733807/\">围观：不同年龄的女性对“碧池”的反应</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p733827/\">别人家的高考 英美大学入学考试盘点</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjengl