  "description": "<p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/fanli/201307/b0b5c97a-8a9c-4542-b4f4-3890c2f1109d.jpg\" style=\"height: 300px; width: 400px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p731816\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tWell, I took advantages of fact it was science <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/fiction\" target=\"_blank\">fiction</a> to be able to <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/escape\" target=\"_blank\">escape</a> from the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/immediate\" target=\"_blank\">immediate</a> press of the issues you just mentioned which I call mind change, and draw analogies of the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/climate\" target=\"_blank\">climate</a> change. What I wanted to do was to let my imagination roam more freely and go over a century into the future to think if we can get beyond the immediate screen technologies, what would people be like. And what I suggest is that, after a while, everyone becomes so standardised. It's not worth communicating with each other, or being <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/hyperconnected\" target=\"_blank\">hyperconnected</a> with each other. So the reverse occurs, some people lead this rather isolated, very sybaritic life. But because you can't just have people having fun, that's not much of a story, what I wanted to do was to introduce conflicting element, and so two generations earlier, there were a very <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/fundamentalist\" target=\"_blank\">fundamentalist</a> group called the Neo-Pures/the Neo-Platonics, who was the very opposite, who actually put a preview on abstract thought on finding out about how the brain worked, and they embarked on a great <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/exodus\" target=\"_blank\">exodus</a>, and the hero is a brain scientist with eerily similar views on the brain to myself, who's then dispatched back across the mountains to try and take over this large group called the Others, and to try to find out how their brains are working.</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身不存储、控制、修改被链接的内容。&ldquo;沪江</span><a class=\"creatLinks\" href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/tag/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"更多英语内容\">英语</a><span>&rdquo;高度重视知识产权保护。当如发现本网站发布的信息包含有侵犯其著作权的链接内容时，请联系我们，我们将依法采取措施移除相关内容或屏蔽相关链接。</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p731816/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p731816\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p733679/\">哈佛情商测试，满分200，你得了多少？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p733875/\">13句受用终生的人生格言</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p733814/\">英语中12个典型的中国式错误是哪些？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p733346/\">像娜塔莉波特曼般聪明？这5类书最能提高IQ</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p733967/\">心都萌化了！英国小王子轻吻妹妹</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p731795/\">美女们请注意！千万别在简历上附照片！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p732912/\">全球海选：生命中最寻常的幸福小事</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p733963/\">励志！英截肢姑娘变身美艳模特</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p733807/\">围观：不同年龄的女性对“碧池”的反应</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p733827/\">别人家的高考